# 🧠 LEVI-AI Sovereign Monolith v13.0.0 - Configuration Template
# Graduate Specification: Optimized for D:\ drive localization & 100% Local Inference.

# ── 1. COGNITIVE SECRETS (EXTERNAL Fallback - NOT REQUIRED for v13 Pulse) ──
